ps://stackofthefuture.com/series/pizza/pizza-1/</guid><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2019 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;In this lesson you will learn how to create basic GraphQL schema for Pizza menu. After that we will deploy a mock backend out of it and proceed to GraphiQL playground to learn GraphQL Query Language. &lt;/p&gt;
